# CurveLens Corn cron template — intentionally non-executable.
#
# Corn is experimental. Do not register or enable schedules from this file.
# A future schedule must start an isolated agent turn, read AGENTS.md plus
# deployments/corn/AGENTS.md, set CCVM_PRODUCT=corn, acquire and verify the
# exact Section 56 bulletin, and invoke `$curvelens-daily-analysis` for its
# internal trade date. It must resume persisted state and perform no delivery
# by default. A bare Python cron is unsupported.
